      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "HI benchmark comparison against FDA experimental dataset — centrifugal pump at 5000 RPM, 5 L/min"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-mesh-sensitivity",
